### Get all - page 1, 10 per page, sorted by display order
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/categories?page=1&size=10&sort=displayOrder,asc

### Get all active
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/categories?active=true&page=1&size=10

### Get all inactive
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/categories?active=false&page=1&size=10